{"tid":1533421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角即時】浸大學生會會長方仲賢被警方以盜竊罪拘捕","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:42:40.000Z","uid":38954,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2dde0426c6045ca7635d296c3c8ece8e6328d3","tid":1533421,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又亂9拉人<br />\n<br />\n浸大學生會會長方仲賢被警方搜查後被捕，警方於方仲賢背囊中找到不屬於本人的財物，是故以盜竊罪名將他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事源為有浸大同學參與中大罷課後遺漏財物，方仲賢代為帶回浸大，惟途中遇到警方搜查。"},{"pid":"25b6e1f1469b00107c99434f021b89f68346dcd2","tid":1533421,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"on9完未"},{"pid":"c3f7b0251a856391478ad3888d2d155f1fccc299","tid":1533421,"uid":80528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"九月三日 三罷<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3S6Hdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3S6Hdd.jpg&h=b77572cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n光復香港 清算警察 人人有責"},{"pid":"fbccd0bb1282efd68b3c657b96e8e4e36543070d","tid":1533421,"uid":164166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59028b7e86689e7140cd3643676c7d84702da28","tid":1533421,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"175505521061c620c99a5d6f815a7ef5802d908d","tid":1533421,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"點解班狗咁鍾意咬住佢，定佢防禦意識唔夠。<br />\n其他大學學生會向浸大交流下"},{"pid":"e740548b8931c97ff34d57d56b4cba2a5cf547a2","tid":1533421,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"175505521061c620c99a5d6f815a7ef5802d908d","tid":1533421,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor